      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASCINATE SAMUEL (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his dynamic win the start prior, getting around The Gardens over 600m in 34.33. Can return to winning form here if runs up to time two back. RISE UP NISMO (6) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 6 lengths (24.95) at Maitland. Has definite claims again. DING'S SANDY (3) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when seventh (30.70) in a Grade 5 at this track. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from three starts. Great chance to atone. WOOLGOOLGA (4) will give backers a sight.",
